API: Empty Vectors
-----------------

`empty` a Vector whose domain is `false` (defined at *no* key)

<br>

\begin{code}
{-@ empty :: forall <p :: Int -> a -> Prop>. 
               Vec <{v:Int|false}, p> a     @-}

empty     = V $ \_ -> error "empty vector!"
\end{code}

